1
00:00:10,111 --> 00:00:13,114
(baby voice)

2
00:00:27,628 --> 00:00:32,633
(baby voice)

3
00:00:38,139 --> 00:00:40,574
(Seiichi) Aiko!

4
00:00:40,641 --> 00:00:44,645
I’m really sorry… I’m sorry!

5
00:00:48,149 --> 00:00:53,654
(Seiichi) Please, please tell me the truth!

6
00:00:55,656 --> 00:00:58,659
I won't move until you tell me the truth.

7
00:01:01,662 --> 00:01:04,532
(Aiko) Hey... just stop.

8
00:01:04,598 --> 00:01:08,536
(Seiichi) It was my fault... No, I was an idiot.

9
00:01:08,602 --> 00:01:12,540
(cry)

10
00:01:12,606 --> 00:01:15,543
I don't need you to forgive me.

11
00:01:15,609 --> 00:01:18,112
It's okay to hate me, I'll do anything.

12
00:01:20,114 --> 00:01:24,618
So... please...

13
00:01:28,122 --> 00:01:33,627
(Seiichi) Please give me a chance.

14
00:01:36,130 --> 00:01:39,066
(Aiko) ⟨6th year...⟩

15
00:01:39,133 --> 00:01:43,070
⟨For 6 years since we got married →

16
00:01:43,137 --> 00:01:46,640
I have been deceived by this husband⟩

17
00:01:49,643 --> 00:01:54,582
(Aiko) ⟨My husband married me for one reason⟩

18
00:01:54,648 --> 00:01:58,085
⟨It was just camouflage⟩

19
00:01:58,152 --> 00:02:07,595
♪～

20
00:02:20,608 --> 00:02:27,615
📱(vibration sound)

21
00:02:29,617 --> 00:02:31,552
(Aiko) Hello, mother-in-law?

22
00:02:31,619 --> 00:02:34,054
📱(Akiko) Hello, Aiko-san.

23
00:02:34,121 --> 00:02:38,058
(Akiko) My father is going to go back to Japan temporarily this weekend.→

24
00:02:38,125 --> 00:02:42,062
If you'd like, why don't you come and see Seiichi?

25
00:02:42,129 --> 00:02:46,066
(Aiko) Sorry, I think that's difficult.

26
00:02:46,133 --> 00:02:48,068
>> Ah, that's a shame.

27
00:02:48,135 --> 00:02:50,070
copper? recently.

28
00:02:50,137 --> 00:02:54,575
(Aiko) Yes... There's no change.

29
00:02:54,642 --> 00:02:57,077
📱 Yes.

30
00:02:57,144 --> 00:02:59,079
📱 Hey Aiko-san?

31
00:02:59,146 --> 00:03:00,581
(Aiko) Yes.

32
00:03:00,648 --> 00:03:05,019
>> If you have any questions, please contact me anytime.

33
00:03:05,085 --> 00:03:07,521
(Aiko) Thank you.

34
00:03:07,588 --> 00:03:10,524
Please give my regards to your father-in-law as well.

35
00:03:10,591 --> 00:03:13,594
Now, excuse me.

36
00:03:21,602 --> 00:03:23,037
(Aiko) Huh...｡

37
00:03:23,103 --> 00:03:27,041
(The sound of the front door opening and closing)

38
00:03:27,107 --> 00:03:29,543
(The sound of running footsteps)

39
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:30,878
(Seiichi) Aiko: What do you mean?

40
00:03:30,945 --> 00:03:33,714
(Aiko) Welcome back. It's great.

41
00:03:33,781 --> 00:03:37,217
Dinner is now ready.

42
00:03:37,718 --> 00:03:40,287
(Seiichi) My subordinate contacted me and you gave me some strange proof→

43
00:03:40,354 --> 00:03:41,855
What do you mean by being sent?

44
00:03:41,922 --> 00:03:44,525
(Aiko) Ah~ Maybe →

45
00:03:44,592 --> 00:03:48,529
Are you talking about that that has reached Seiichi too?

46
00:03:48,596 --> 00:04:08,148
♪～

47
00:04:08,215 --> 00:04:10,651
(Seiichi) What is this? Don't be silly!

48
00:04:11,051 --> 00:04:12,486
(Aiko) Divorced.

49
00:04:12,553 --> 00:04:14,221
(Seiichi) In that case, we should just talk about it. This is meaningless →

50
00:04:14,288 --> 00:04:16,223
What are you going to do with all this nonsense?

51
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:19,727
(Aiko) Doesn't it make sense? Is it boring?

52
00:04:19,793 --> 00:04:21,729
Even though I had an affair!

53
00:04:21,795 --> 00:04:26,233
Do you think I'll never know anything?

54
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:29,236
(Seiichi) It only happened once. Adultery isn't such a big deal.

55
00:04:29,303 --> 00:04:31,238
(Aiko) Hmm.

56
00:04:31,305 --> 00:04:34,742
Just one time and you're a baby.

57
00:04:34,808 --> 00:04:39,313
I'm glad my favorite girlfriend has a baby.

58
00:04:41,315 --> 00:04:43,250
Ah, but during this time→

59
00:04:43,317 --> 00:04:48,756
Did you drop the child without telling Seiichi?

60
00:04:48,822 --> 00:04:53,761
Apparently it was inconvenient to have a child with me →

61
00:04:54,328 --> 00:04:58,265
Did you really hate her pregnancy?

62
00:04:58,332 --> 00:05:01,502
(Seiichi) That's not what we're talking about right now.

63
00:05:01,568 --> 00:05:06,440
Before you do this! Should you talk to me?

64
00:05:06,507 --> 00:05:08,942
(Aiko) What will happen if I tell you that you won't listen?

65
00:05:09,009 --> 00:05:11,445
(Seiichi) Of course they're a couple, you idiot! Something like this!

66
00:05:11,512 --> 00:05:14,515
(Aiko) Which one is stupid? (sound of hitting)

67
00:05:16,517 --> 00:05:21,021
(Seiichi) Hahaha...｡

68
00:05:25,526 --> 00:05:27,961
📱(Camera shutter sound)

69
00:05:28,028 --> 00:05:31,465
(Seiichi) What are you doing? (Aiko) Evidence.

70
00:05:31,532 --> 00:05:34,034
I have to take a picture while the blood is still flowing.

71
00:05:35,536 --> 00:05:39,540
I've been suffering all this time.

72
00:05:42,543 --> 00:05:45,045
(Aiko) My decision will not change.

73
00:05:47,047 --> 00:05:49,483
(Seiichi) Aiko, let's talk.

74
00:05:49,550 --> 00:05:51,485
Calm down...

75
00:05:51,552 --> 00:05:52,553
Lend it to me. (Aiko) Stop it.

76
00:05:52,653 --> 00:05:53,487
(Seiichi) Lend it to me. (Aiko) Stop it!

77
00:05:53,554 --> 00:05:57,991
(Seiichi) Lend it to me! (Aiko) Stop it! Don't come near me!

78
00:05:58,058 --> 00:06:00,494
I'm recording everything.

79
00:06:00,561 --> 00:06:02,996
I won't be fooled anymore.

80
00:06:03,063 --> 00:06:07,935
You only saw her before you got married.

81
00:06:08,001 --> 00:06:10,938
You married me to get promoted, right?

82
00:06:11,004 --> 00:06:13,640
I'm just a disposable tool for that purpose.

83
00:06:13,707 --> 00:06:16,210
(Seiichi) It didn't matter who it was... (Aiko) I looked into it!

84
00:06:18,779 --> 00:06:21,281
Because I know everything.

85
00:06:24,785 --> 00:06:26,720
(Ayaka) What do you mean by everything?

86
00:06:26,787 --> 00:06:30,224
(Seiichi) I don't know. When did you know?

87
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:35,229
But I also knew that we were dating before we got married.

88
00:06:35,295 --> 00:06:38,732
(Ayaka) Hey, that girl did it unexpectedly.

89
00:06:38,799 --> 00:06:41,735
I thought you were insensitive and didn't even notice.

90
00:06:41,802 --> 00:06:43,737
(Seiichi) Are you saying such carefree things?

91
00:06:43,804 --> 00:06:45,739
>> There's no point in panicking.

92
00:06:45,806 --> 00:06:48,742
But…｡ (sound of beer can being opened)

93
00:06:48,809 --> 00:06:51,745
(Ayaka) It's disgusting.

94
00:06:51,812 --> 00:06:53,514
(Seiichi) Is it okay to drink alcohol?

95
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:56,517
>> Don't worry, I'm not sick.

96
00:06:57,251 --> 00:07:03,190
I definitely don't want to pay 10 million yen more than that.

97
00:07:03,257 --> 00:07:06,126
(Seiichi) I understand.

98
00:07:06,593 --> 00:07:09,096
I'll do something.

99
00:07:14,735 --> 00:07:17,171
(Aiko) Grandma.

100
00:07:17,237 --> 00:07:19,740
Please protect me.

101
00:07:22,242 --> 00:07:24,978
(sound of door opening)

102
00:07:25,045 --> 00:07:27,481
(Aiko) Good morning, let's eat breakfast.

103
00:07:27,981 --> 00:07:28,782
(Seiichi) Huh?

104
00:07:28,849 --> 00:07:32,286
(Aiko) I thought I'd go back to change clothes, so I prepared some.

105
00:07:32,352 --> 00:07:34,855
yeah? What if I sit down?

106
00:07:36,356 --> 00:07:38,358
Okay...｡

107
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,362
I'll enjoy having this.

108
00:07:44,364 --> 00:07:48,302
(Seiichi) The discussion is going well. (Aiko) Yeah, that's right.

109
00:07:48,368 --> 00:07:50,804
(Seiichi) But before that, can we talk together?

110
00:07:50,871 --> 00:07:53,807
(Aiko) I can't do anything for my convenience.

111
00:07:53,874 --> 00:07:56,810
(Seiichi) I admit to cheating.

112
00:07:56,877 --> 00:07:59,313
But from someone I've only met a few times →

113
00:07:59,379 --> 00:08:01,815
It would be strange to get 10 million yen.

114
00:08:01,882 --> 00:08:04,751
(Aiko) Only a few times.

115
00:08:05,419 --> 00:08:07,187
Were you dating before you got married?

116
00:08:07,254 --> 00:08:10,357
(Seiichi) No, that's why... (Aiko) I'm sorry, but→

117
00:08:10,424 --> 00:08:13,861
I won't give up on the terms of the divorce.

118
00:08:13,927 --> 00:08:17,431
I look forward to discussing it tomorrow.

119
00:08:19,933 --> 00:08:22,936
Ah, that's right.

120
00:08:27,441 --> 00:08:31,378
(Aiko) Yes, lunch box.

121
00:08:31,445 --> 00:08:35,883
yeah? You like fried chicken bento, right?

122
00:08:35,949 --> 00:08:38,385
(Seiichi) What do you mean?

123
00:08:38,452 --> 00:08:42,890
(Aiko) We became husband and wife through some kind of fate, right?

124
00:08:42,956 --> 00:08:45,392
You have to take care of your relationships.

125
00:08:45,459 --> 00:08:48,896
Until the divorce is finalized →

126
00:08:48,962 --> 00:08:53,400
I want my wife to do her job properly.

127
00:08:53,467 --> 00:08:55,402
Hmm.

128
00:08:55,469 --> 00:09:23,363
♪～

129
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:26,366
(Aiko) You're a liar...

130
00:09:26,433 --> 00:09:29,870
(camera shutter sound)

131
00:09:29,937 --> 00:09:32,372
(Okada) There is a danger to your life.

132
00:09:32,439 --> 00:09:34,875
Don't overdo it. (Aiko) It's okay.

133
00:09:34,942 --> 00:09:36,877
(Okada) Aiko-san doesn't know.

134
00:09:36,944 --> 00:09:39,880
A furious husband doesn't know what to do.

135
00:09:39,947 --> 00:09:42,382
(Aiko) Yes. (Camera shutter sound)

136
00:09:42,449 --> 00:09:44,885
(Aiko) But I took the photo with my smartphone.

137
00:09:44,952 --> 00:09:45,585
(sound of door opening)

138
00:09:45,652 --> 00:09:50,257
(Yuki) It's different when you take pictures with a proper camera, Mr. Okada.

139
00:09:50,324 --> 00:09:51,725
(Aiko) Hello, Mr. Yuki.

140
00:09:51,792 --> 00:09:56,229
>> Hello... Are you okay!? Terrible bruise.

141
00:09:56,296 --> 00:09:59,232
(Okada) Director, please take care of yourself. (Aiko) It's really okay.

142
00:09:59,299 --> 00:10:01,735
(Okada) I can't trust Aiko's "it's okay" statement.

143
00:10:01,802 --> 00:10:04,738
>> What the lawyer in charge says is absolutely true, Aiko-san.

144
00:10:04,805 --> 00:10:07,741
(Okada) If you don't want to treat a wound, try Razon's cream puffs →

145
00:10:07,808 --> 00:10:10,243
I'll leave it to you, right? Mr. Seo.

146
00:10:10,310 --> 00:10:14,247
(Seo) That's right, Aiko-san. (Aiko) Eh, eh...｡

147
00:10:14,314 --> 00:10:17,751
(Seo) Well! It's rare!

148
00:10:17,818 --> 00:10:19,753
(Aiko) Were you able to buy Razon cream puffs?

149
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:21,755
(Okada) We lined up 30 minutes before the store opened.

150
00:10:21,822 --> 00:10:23,757
>> As expected of a sweets boy.

151
00:10:23,824 --> 00:10:27,761
(Aiko) Hahaha...! Oh, sorry.

152
00:10:27,828 --> 00:10:31,765
Just imagine the teacher standing in line.

153
00:10:31,832 --> 00:10:34,334
(Okada) It's okay. You don't have to eat it. (Aiko) I'll eat it!

154
00:10:34,801 --> 00:10:39,940
(Yuki) Before that, let's get some treatment. (Aiko) Yes.

155
00:10:42,042 --> 00:10:46,046
(Okada) Mr. Seiichi informed me that he would agree to discuss tomorrow.

156
00:10:46,113 --> 00:10:51,051
However, it seems that Ayaka Ando would also like to be present for the discussion.

157
00:10:51,118 --> 00:10:53,086
(Aiko) It seems like she was worried about money →

158
00:10:53,153 --> 00:10:55,822
I thought that might happen.

159
00:10:55,889 --> 00:10:58,325
(Okada) Aiko-san, are you okay with that?

160
00:10:58,392 --> 00:11:00,327
>> You can also refuse.

161
00:11:00,394 --> 00:11:04,831
With Mr. Seiichi, we are talking about divorce, and with Mr. Ando, ​​we are talking about money.→

162
00:11:04,898 --> 00:11:07,334
It's better to talk separately →

163
00:11:07,401 --> 00:11:09,269
And Aiko-san too →

164
00:11:09,336 --> 00:11:12,773
You don't want to see the face of the person you're having an affair with.

165
00:11:13,306 --> 00:11:18,245
(Aiko) I would like to see the two of them together.

166
00:11:18,311 --> 00:11:21,815
What kind of face will you appear in front of me?

167
00:11:25,318 --> 00:11:26,586
(Okada) Understood.

168
00:11:26,653 --> 00:11:29,089
Let's check what we'll talk about tomorrow.

169
00:11:29,856 --> 00:11:31,858
(Aiko) Yes.

170
00:11:36,296 --> 00:11:38,732
>> You have become stronger, Aiko-san.

171
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:41,735
It's completely different from when I came to my house two years ago.

172
00:11:41,802 --> 00:11:44,237
(Okada) Yes, I can feel their determination.

173
00:11:44,304 --> 00:11:47,307
As expected of Aiko.

174
00:12:06,326 --> 00:12:08,862
(Seiichi) Yes, it's a gift to commemorate our first date.

175
00:12:08,929 --> 00:12:10,864
(Aiko) I can't have that.

176
00:12:10,931 --> 00:12:14,868
I'll pay the money... (Seiichi) Haha, Mr. Ayukawa is serious.

177
00:12:14,935 --> 00:12:17,871
Well, how about I say thank you for going on a date today?

178
00:12:17,938 --> 00:12:20,941
(Aiko) Thank you so much...

179
00:12:24,444 --> 00:12:27,380
(Seiichi) It was love at first sight.

180
00:12:27,447 --> 00:12:30,383
Look, Mr. Ayukawa gave you his business card earlier.

181
00:12:30,450 --> 00:12:33,386
I've been curious about it ever since.

182
00:12:34,121 --> 00:12:40,060
I often saw him eating his lunch on the bench at noon.

183
00:12:44,064 --> 00:12:49,603
(firework)

184
00:12:49,669 --> 00:12:51,605
(Aiko) Beautiful...｡

185
00:12:51,671 --> 00:13:04,117
♪～

186
00:13:04,184 --> 00:13:06,620
(Seiichi) Um...

187
00:13:06,686 --> 00:13:10,190
Please date me with the intention of marriage.

188
00:13:14,694 --> 00:13:18,632
(Seiichi) Sorry, you can always reply... (Aiko) No, no, um... that's not true.

189
00:13:18,698 --> 00:13:22,702
That... I was surprised.

190
00:13:26,706 --> 00:13:30,143
(Aiko) Yes, please.

191
00:13:35,148 --> 00:13:38,084
(firework)

192
00:13:45,659 --> 00:13:49,162
(Aiko)《It was all a lie》

193
00:14:03,677 --> 00:14:06,613
(Okada) This is the result of the investigation.

194
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:09,616
Seiichi's cheating partner is Ayaka Ando.

195
00:14:09,683 --> 00:14:12,619
I am two years my junior at the same company.

196
00:14:12,686 --> 00:14:16,122
(Aiko) Yes, I know.

197
00:14:16,189 --> 00:14:20,126
(Okada) The relationship between the two began the year Ando joined the company.

198
00:14:20,193 --> 00:14:22,128
In other words →

199
00:14:22,195 --> 00:14:25,632
It was long before you and Seiichi met.

200
00:14:25,699 --> 00:14:27,133
(Aiko) Huh...｡

201
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,636
(Okada) Also on the night before the wedding →

202
00:14:29,703 --> 00:14:33,139
In the name of Ayaka Ando at the hotel that served as the reception venue →

203
00:14:33,206 --> 00:14:36,576
I found out that a double room was booked.

204
00:14:36,643 --> 00:14:40,080
In the room service history, there is a payment for a meal for two →

205
00:14:40,146 --> 00:14:45,085
There was a record of Seiichi's credit card being used.

206
00:14:45,151 --> 00:14:50,090
(Aiko) In other words, the two of us stayed at a hotel the night before the wedding →

207
00:14:50,156 --> 00:14:53,593
From there, I came to the ceremony hall where my wedding would be held →

208
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:56,596
Do you mean...?

209
00:14:56,663 --> 00:14:59,599
(Okada) Yes.

210
00:14:59,666 --> 00:15:01,668
(Aiko) 《Liar》

211
00:15:08,675 --> 00:15:10,610
(Okada) [Mr. Seiichi and Mr. Ando →

212
00:15:10,677 --> 00:15:14,614
We have never broken up our relationship even after we got married.

213
00:15:14,681 --> 00:15:20,620
[They have been dating since before marriage until now.]

214
00:15:20,687 --> 00:15:26,626
[This was a marriage arranged from the beginning.]

215
00:15:26,693 --> 00:15:31,131
(Aiko) A liar...a liar...｡

216
00:15:31,197 --> 00:15:35,068
Liar Liar Liar Liar →

217
00:15:35,135 --> 00:15:37,570
Liar! Liar!

218
00:15:37,637 --> 00:15:39,139
Huh...

219
00:15:41,141 --> 00:15:46,579
《My husband has been thinking about me from the beginning →

220
00:15:46,646 --> 00:15:49,149
I didn't love you

221
00:15:52,018 --> 00:15:55,955
(Sound of door opening) (Salesperson) Welcome.

222
00:16:03,697 --> 00:16:08,134
(Aiko) 《My husband is with a woman who is not me》

223
00:16:08,201 --> 00:16:10,103
(Salesperson) Excuse me.

224
00:16:10,170 --> 00:16:12,605
I'd like to take your order. (Seiichi) Iced coffee and...

225
00:16:12,672 --> 00:16:17,110
(Aiko) 《Is this man really my husband?》

226
00:16:17,177 --> 00:16:21,181
(gurgle gurgle…)

227
00:16:24,184 --> 00:16:27,120
(Okada) I will be in charge of representing Aiko.→

228
00:16:27,187 --> 00:16:29,689
I'm Okada, a lawyer.

229
00:16:31,191 --> 00:16:35,628
Right away, the fact that you two came together is →

230
00:16:35,695 --> 00:16:38,131
Is it okay to understand that we are friends like that?

231
00:16:38,198 --> 00:16:40,133
(Seiichi) No!

232
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:43,636
When it comes to adultery, it's just a misunderstanding on your part.

233
00:16:44,437 --> 00:16:47,941
You're just a subordinate, but you're causing trouble.

234
00:16:51,945 --> 00:16:54,814
(Seiichi) Today I would like to explain that and have it withdrawn→

235
00:16:54,881 --> 00:16:57,617
I was asked to sit with you.

236
00:16:57,684 --> 00:17:02,188
If you're having an affair, you can't bring him in openly.

237
00:17:05,692 --> 00:17:08,628
(Okada) Right away →

238
00:17:08,695 --> 00:17:11,197
This is a report of the investigation results.

239
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:17,637
(Okada) There are multiple pieces of evidence that determine the relationship between the two of you.

240
00:17:17,704 --> 00:17:19,639
I wrote it there too →

241
00:17:19,706 --> 00:17:23,643
The night before the wedding, in the double room of the hotel that served as the reception venue →

242
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:26,146
You two are staying together.

243
00:17:26,212 --> 00:17:29,649
(Seiichi) That's to get them to attend the reception →

244
00:17:29,716 --> 00:17:31,651
I'm not staying the night.

245
00:17:31,718 --> 00:17:35,155
(Okada) Have room service with a woman who is not your wife the night before the wedding?

246
00:17:35,822 --> 00:17:38,258
And even breakfast.

247
00:17:38,324 --> 00:17:41,394
(Seiichi) I just had a meal. (Okada) Even in the credits for the past six years →

248
00:17:41,461 --> 00:17:44,397
You've done quite a bit of shopping.

249
00:17:44,464 --> 00:17:48,902
Ah, that's a Rolique bag.

250
00:17:48,968 --> 00:17:51,404
Purchase history of exactly the same item →

251
00:17:51,471 --> 00:17:55,842
It was on Mr. Sasashima's credit card statement.

252
00:17:55,909 --> 00:17:57,844
That's not all.

253
00:17:57,911 --> 00:18:02,348
There are multiple purchases of expensive accessories and shoes.

254
00:18:02,415 --> 00:18:04,851
I checked with Aiko →

255
00:18:04,918 --> 00:18:09,355
It seems like he never received one from you.

256
00:18:09,422 --> 00:18:12,859
(Seiichi) That's...→

257
00:18:12,926 --> 00:18:16,930
I handed it out to my junior colleagues at the company.

258
00:18:20,934 --> 00:18:22,936
(Okada) Mr. Ando.

259
00:18:24,437 --> 00:18:28,875
You got pregnant a while ago, right?

260
00:18:28,942 --> 00:18:31,945
It has been confirmed.

261
00:18:33,947 --> 00:18:37,383
At Aiko's request that it be peaceful →

262
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:40,386
This is how we set up a place for discussion.

263
00:18:40,453 --> 00:18:44,891
If you don't accept it, we'll go to court.

264
00:18:44,958 --> 00:18:48,895
If it goes to court, I don't know where or how it will be reported to the company.

265
00:18:48,962 --> 00:18:52,899
However, if there is a conflict of opinion →

266
00:18:52,966 --> 00:18:55,401
It would be unavoidable.

267
00:18:59,405 --> 00:19:01,341
>> That...

268
00:19:01,407 --> 00:19:03,343
(Okada) Yes.

269
00:19:03,409 --> 00:19:05,912
>> The company...

270
00:19:07,914 --> 00:19:09,849
Can I ask you to do so in confidence?

271
00:19:09,916 --> 00:19:13,853
(Seiichi) I would also like to ask a favor.

272
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:16,856
(Okada) It's up to Aiko.

273
00:19:16,923 --> 00:19:22,862
(Aiko) I want to get divorced as soon as possible.

274
00:19:22,929 --> 00:19:26,366
Going to court will take a long time.

275
00:19:26,432 --> 00:19:28,368
If you don't want the company to find out →

276
00:19:28,434 --> 00:19:32,939
Please agree to divorce and tell the truth.

277
00:19:42,448 --> 00:19:46,386
(gurgle gurgle…)

278
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:49,055
(Seiichi's voice) I admit it.

279
00:19:49,122 --> 00:19:51,624
(gurgling…)

280
00:19:52,458 --> 00:19:54,827
(Seiichi) Before marriage →

281
00:19:54,894 --> 00:19:58,831
I was in a relationship with Mr. Ando.

282
00:19:58,898 --> 00:20:01,834
Actually, I proposed to her →

283
00:20:01,901 --> 00:20:05,338
Mr. Ando prioritizes work→

284
00:20:05,405 --> 00:20:09,842
I said that marriage was still a long way off...

285
00:20:09,909 --> 00:20:14,347
(Aiko) 《The person I loved the most was right in front of me→

286
00:20:14,414 --> 00:20:19,919
Talking while holding hands with someone you truly love

287
00:20:21,921 --> 00:20:25,425
(Seiichi) I feel sorry for my wife.

288
00:20:30,930 --> 00:20:33,866
(Okada) May I ask you one question?

289
00:20:34,634 --> 00:20:36,002
(Seiichi) Yes.

290
00:20:36,069 --> 00:20:39,005
(Okada) Did you marry Aiko even though there was no love from the beginning?

291
00:20:39,072 --> 00:20:41,007
(Seiichi) That's...

292
00:20:41,074 --> 00:20:54,954
♪～

293
00:20:55,021 --> 00:20:57,457
(Aiko) Excuse me. (Salesclerk) Yes.

294
00:20:57,523 --> 00:20:59,959
(Aiko) Could you please raise the temperature just a little?

295
00:21:00,026 --> 00:21:01,527
>> Understood.

296
00:21:05,531 --> 00:21:07,967
(Salesperson) Please use this if you like.

297
00:21:08,034 --> 00:21:10,970
(Aiko) Ah, then to her.

298
00:21:11,037 --> 00:21:12,972
(Salesperson) Please.

299
00:21:13,039 --> 00:21:16,976
(Aiko) You look pale.

300
00:21:17,043 --> 00:21:21,981
You're not feeling well yet, are you?

301
00:21:22,048 --> 00:21:25,051
I just had an abortion.

302
00:21:28,554 --> 00:21:30,490
(Aiko) Ah...

303
00:21:30,556 --> 00:21:32,892
(Okada) Are you okay? (Aiko) Ah... Thank you.

304
00:21:32,959 --> 00:21:34,961
>> lowest!

305
00:21:38,865 --> 00:21:45,304
(Aiko) Teacher: I have no intention of lowering the compensation by one yen.

306
00:21:45,371 --> 00:21:48,808
If you don't want the company to find out, make a quick decision.

307
00:21:48,875 --> 00:21:51,310
Please tell that to the other person.

308
00:21:51,377 --> 00:21:52,812
(Sound of putting down a cup)

309
00:21:52,879 --> 00:21:58,751
♪～

310
00:21:58,818 --> 00:22:00,753
(Seiichi) Excuse me.

311
00:22:00,820 --> 00:22:05,758
♪～

312
00:22:05,825 --> 00:22:07,627
(gurgling…)

313
00:22:07,694 --> 00:22:12,131
(Aiko) 《What has my life been like so far?》

314
00:22:12,198 --> 00:22:14,133
《Betrayed? 》

315
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:18,638
《The wrong husband did not betray me》

316
00:22:18,705 --> 00:22:23,142
《You didn't even love me from the beginning》

317
00:22:23,209 --> 00:22:28,014
♪～

318
00:22:28,081 --> 00:22:30,016
(Aiko) Seiichi-san.

319
00:22:30,083 --> 00:22:46,032
♪～

320
00:22:46,099 --> 00:22:48,101
(Aiko) 《I love you》

321
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:58,678
(Aiko) ⟨This is my husband and I who loved each other so much that we wanted to kill them →

322
00:22:58,745 --> 00:23:01,748
It is a story of rebirth⟩
